# NI USB-6009 Logger (AI + DI)

CLI to log NI USB-6009 analog inputs and optional digital inputs to CSV/XLSX with progress and preview.

## Features
- AI (hardware-timed) + DI (static snapshot per AI chunk)
- CSV or XLSX
- Progress counter/bar, `--print-first N` preview
- Safe filenames (no overwrite)
- Works on Windows with NI-DAQmx

## Install

```powershell
# Create venv (optional)
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\activate

# From source
pip install -e .
# Excel support:
pip install -e .[excel]
